<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بْنِ يَزِيدَ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«حُجَّ بِي مَعَ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> وَأَنَا ابْنُ سَبْعِ سِنِينَ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>